						<h2 class="heading-secondary single-post_title"><a href="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/still-coat-weather/">Still Coat Weather</a></h2>
						<div class="single-post_meta">
							<div class="single-post_meta--date">March 4th, 2015</div>
							<div class="single-post_meta--author">Steve</div>
							<div class="single-post_meta--comments"><a href="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/still-coat-weather/"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="3285 http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/?p=3285">50 Comments</span></a></div>
						</div>
						<div class="single-post_content">
							<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3286" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_1.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_1" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3287" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_2.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_2" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3290" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_5.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_5" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3289" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_4.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_4" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3288" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_3.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_3" width="814" height="543" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3291" src="http://www.stevebooker.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_6.jpg" alt="steve_booker_from_paris_with_love_6" width="814" height="543" />
<p>Nathan is pretty rad. A good coat is an awesome way to finish any outfit. I found this one from A.P.C. (<a href="http://bit.ly/1BSNXKD" target="_blank">similar here</a>) which is definitely one of my favourites right now, as you know I love subtle styling and embellishments, this definitely runs through the A.P.C. which I love. It was the colour that initially jumped out at me as it&#8217;s a<span id="more-3285"></span> great alternative to a dark winter coat. Though the weather is getting slightly warmer now the colour also lends itself to spring pretty well too, so you can lose the jumper / other layers and just wear it with a shirt or t-shirt.  I paired mine up with this Acne shirt (<a href="http://bit.ly/1BSOex5" target="_blank">similar here</a>) and <a href="http://bit.ly/1BSO6O4" target="_blank">jeans</a> (another one of my favourites) and some classic <a href="http://bit.ly/1ElFxu7" target="_blank">Adidas Stan Smiths</a>, which I&#8217;m wearing a ton at the moment.</p>
<p>What&#8217;s been your go to outfit that you&#8217;ve been diggin&#8217; recently?</p>
<p>Steve. x</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
